**Describe your issue**

Hey there. 👋 I've run into an issue where the utility isn't working.

In this example, the `capsized-*` utility does not work with Tailwind version 4.3.0. It is unclear from the release notes whether this change was intentional or a mistake. Thanks!

```
@import "tailwindcss";

@utility capsized-* {
  &::before,
  &::after {
    @apply table content-[""];
  }
  &::before {
    @apply mb-(--capsized);
  }
  &::after {
    @apply mt-(--capsized);
  }
}
@utility capsized-h1 {
  --capsized: -0.08em;
}
@utility capsized-h2 {
  --capsized: -0.09em;
}
@utility capsized-h3 {
  --capsized: -0.09em;
}
```
